                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg><span>Festpreisangebot möglich</span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
